harmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/292702/', '', 'Ezogabine, Ethosuximide, Lacosamide, Levetiracetam, Tiagabine, Ethotoin, Clonazepam, Paramethadione, Ganaxolone, Vigabatrin, Mephenytoin, More', 'Megestrol acetate, Estetrol, Megestrol acetate', 1767369485);
